# Base URL for apps/studio-worker HTTP API (immersive-studio serve).
# Local: http://127.0.0.1:8787
# Production builds (Vercel, etc.): set this to your public worker origin before `vite build`
# — VITE_* is inlined at build time, not read at runtime in the browser.
# Worker must allow the same browser origins via STUDIO_CORS_ORIGINS (comma-separated), e.g.
#   https://your-app.vercel.app,https://www.yourdomain.com
VITE_STUDIO_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787
